Title: Add queue usage counters to status table
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: livestatus
Date: 1667979318
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.2.0b1

Add 6 columns to the status table in livestatus: carbon_queue_usage,
carbon_queue_usage_rate, influxdb_queue_usage, influxdb_queue_usage_rate,
rrdcached_queue_usage, rrdcached_queue_usage_rate.  Usage is defined
as the approximate size of the queue passing the data to its connection
over the total size of the queue.


